<p>数据表批处理操作：</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">numpy</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">np</span>
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">pandas</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">pd</span>

<span class="c1"># data is a dataFrame/ndarray
</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">==</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">1</span> <span class="c1">#change all the 0 into 1
# note: data==0 is a boolen array,which canbe used as index
</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span> <span class="c1">#这个知识点在于np支持批量运算+数组索引
</span></code></pre></div></div>
